\fs29 \cf2 GOD\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Up to this point Elijah has had an incredible few days\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Made fire come down from heaven\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Killed hundreds of prophets who were against God\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Made it rain!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Ended a multi-year drought\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf6 \super 2\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So Jezebel sent a messenger to Elijah to say, \'93May the gods deal with me, be it ever so severely,\'a0if by this time tomorrow I do not make your life like that of one of them.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}No matter what you do, you will always make someone angry!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Here is the Clickbait Headline \'96 I\'92m going to kill you!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Irony:  \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Elijah just killed all her prophets, \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Elijah just saw God do amazing things in incredible ways, \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Elijah just saw God answer his prayers\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}She threatens him against the backdrop of the power of her gods!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf6 \super 3\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Elijah was afraid
\fs15 \super [\ul a\ulnone ]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'a0and ran\'a0for his life.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Past success with God don\'92t equal current faith in God\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But he is blindsided!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He just won in his mind\'85how could someone deny the power of God and so I believe he let\'92s his guard down and gets hit.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Last week we said \'96 
\f5\b \cf7 The enemy inside of you is greater than the enemy in front of you
\f3\b0 \cf2 !\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The threat in front of him is no real threat\'85but the enemy inside of him\'85the Clickbait headlines\'85the fear that comes from the story\'85now that has power!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The Clickbait takes you to a story and that story for Elijah is terrifying\'85to die at her hands.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But what we see here is the up and down spiritual walk when you don\'92t have a handle on the Clickbait\'85it will take you places you don\'92t want to go.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some of you right now this is where you are at.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You have something scary going on that is in front of you\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl2\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You have medical bills and the threat is to kill you financially\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You have a secret, and the threat of someone finding is causing you to behave in odd ways\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You have an opportunity, but there is a threat of failure or loss that seems huge and overwhelming\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You have something you\'92re suppose to do, but the threat of looking foolish is overpowering.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are suppose to share your faith, and there is a threat of relational death\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Steps of Faith \'96 but it will cost us something\
\pard\tx2380\tx2880\pardeftab720\li2880\fi-2880\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl3\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Church starting\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl2\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}ETC\'85(need a few more examples)\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f5\b \cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It may protect you from pain, but will also prevent you from seeing your potential!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b0 \cf6 When he came to Beersheba\'a0in Judah, he left his servant there,\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Elijah leaves others behind.  We don\'92t know why totally but let me say that when you allow the Clickbait to run rampant in your head what happens is you start to seclude yourself from others.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You tell yourself lies like \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl2\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}they won\'92t understand\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I can do this alone\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m better off alone\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They\'92re better off without me\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And without someone there to encourage and pick you up you become even more vulnerable.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Normally at the time we need people the most, we are most opposed to their company.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf6 \super 4\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub while he himself went a day\'92s journey into the wilderness. He came to a broom bush,\'a0sat down under it and prayed that he might die. \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What is he running from?  Someone who wants to kill him.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Why is he running?  He wants to live.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What did he just say?  I want to die.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is irrational and this is what stress and fear combined will do to a person\'85cause them to make irrational decisions.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They will just give up on a dream they\'92ve had for a while\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They will give up on a marriage they\'92ve been fighting for\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They will give on a health initiative they\'92ve been on for months because of one bad day or week\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They will give up on being clean \'96 because of a bad weekend\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They will just give up on life sometimes\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf6 \super 7\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The angel of the\'a0Lord\'a0came back a second time and touched him and said, \'93Get up and eat, for the journey is too much for you.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The journey is too much for you.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some of you need to hear that today\'85your journey is too much for you.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f5\b \cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t do it alone.  \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You need others\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You need God\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You need the church\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f3\b0 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And so if you\'92re here today and tired, not physically, but emotionally and spiritually\'85\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Getting up every day fighting the same battles and same war\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Weary like Elijah then you need to know you\'92re right where God can start to work in your life.  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}See I believe for some, the fear isn\'92t terrifying like a monster, but the fear is about never finding peace in the situation.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Fighting the same battles in your \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}marriage day after day and it\'92s just easier to let it die\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}addiction and it\'92s just easier to give up and let it happen\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}failure and it\'92s just easier to let the dream die\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}etc\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

