\ls9\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs21 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Pause \'96 in the midst of fear and don\'92t freak out but remember who is God\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Remember He hasn\'92t left you\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92re good!\
